Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: rastools
Version: 0.5
Summary: Tools for converting SSRL scans into images
Home-page: https://www.waveform.org.uk/rastools/
Author: Dave Hughes
Author-email: dave@waveform.org.uk
License: UNKNOWN
Description: rastools is a small suite of utilities for converting data files obtained from SSRL (Stanford Synchrotron Radiation Lightsource) scans (.RAS and .DAT files) into images. Various simple manipulations (cropping, percentiles, histograms, color-maps) are supported. Most tools are command line based, but a Qt-based GUI is also included.
